Andiny Atlas Database Migration Guide
=====================================

Create a migration

    alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description"

Apply migrations

    alembic upgrade head

Check migration status

    alembic current

Validate schema

    alembic check

Rollback one revision

    alembic downgrade -1

Migration philosophy

- SQLAlchemy models describe the desired schema.
- Alembic generates migration scripts.
- Every migration is reviewed before execution.
- Application startup never modifies database schema.